data.description:
Priced to sell, this home is not far from the primary school and the Elks Lodge.
The back porch was enclosed for added  square footage and the separate  laundry room includes a half bath.
The back yard is enclosed with a block wall and has a built in grill, as well as a block work shed. 
The AC/Heat pump was installed in 2017, don't wait to long to look at this one!
